high_descs: Turn right and walk down the hallway to reach the brown shelf.
Pick up the bottle with the golden top on the left of the shelf.
Turn around and take a right turn at the end of the passage to enter the bedroom to face the table on the right.
Switch on the table lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the bottle with the golden top under the lamp light.

high_descs: Move ahead, turn to your right, move straight towards the shelf
Pick up the bottle on the shelf
Turn around, walk straight toward the end, then turn to your right, move ahead, turn to your right, move towards the table
Turn on the small lamp on the table
anns.task_desc: Examine the bottle by the small lamp on the table

high_descs: Walk out of room to right to the shelf.
Pick up the gold item on the shelf.
Turn go to last bedroom on right.
Stand in front of desk.
anns.task_desc: Turn right in to hallway grab gold item off shelf, take with to desk in last bedroom on right.

high_descs: Head towards the door, then turn around and move towards the steel shelf.
Pick the battery lamp from the saltshaker rack.
Turn around and head towards the desklamp.
Place the battery desklamp on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the shelf on your right.
Pick up a salt shaker from shelf.
Go straight and turn right, head straight and hang right, head straight to the desk lamp
Turn on the desk lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a salt shaker by the light of a desk lamp.
